<div>
    <h1 id="wilday-ui-button">Wilday UI Button Component</h1>

    <h2 id="copy-to-clipboard">Copy to Clipboard</h2>
    <p>Copy text to clipboard with a feedback message.</p>

    <div class="separator"></div>

    <h3 id="api-reference">API Reference</h3>
    <div class="api-reference">
        <p>The <code>copy_to_clipboard</code> option accepts either a string or a hash with the following properties:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><code>text</code> (String) - The text to be copied</li>
            <li><code>feedback_text</code> (String, optional) - Custom feedback message (default: "Copied!")</li>
            <li><code>position</code> (String, optional) - Position of the feedback tooltip. Options:
                <ul>
                    <li><code>top</code>, <code>top-start</code>, <code>top-center</code>, <code>top-end</code></li>
                    <li><code>bottom</code>, <code>bottom-start</code>, <code>bottom-center</code>, <code>bottom-end</code></li>
                    <li><code>left</code>, <code>right</code></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><code>duration</code> (Number, optional) - Duration in milliseconds to show feedback (default: 2000)</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="separator"></div>

    <h3 id="basic-usage-default">Basic usage - Default</h3>
    <div class="component-example">
        <div class="component-preview">
            <%= w_button "Copy",
                copy_to_clipboard: "Text to copy",
                variant: :outline,
                icon: "fa-solid fa-clipboard"
            %>
        </div>

        <div class="component-code">
<pre><code class="language-ruby"><%%= w_button "Copy",
    copy_to_clipboard: "Text to copy",
    variant: :outline,
    icon: "fa-solid fa-clipboard"
%></code></pre>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="separator"></div>

